values
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-mirror', 1, 'Tender Mirror', 'You are allowed to meet yourself with less pressure today. Offer yourself the same patience you keep giving away.', 'Inner kindness changes the pace of healing because it removes the need to fight yourself. Return to what helps you feel held rather than evaluated.', 'self-love', 'soft reset', 'self-love/tender-mirror', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-return', 2, 'Tender Return', 'Notice what relaxes your body when no one is watching. Your worth does not rise and fall with productivity.', 'When you stop managing how lovable you appear, your energy becomes more whole. For now, let one decision today be shaped by self-respect instead of self-pressure.', 'self-love', 'quiet confidence', 'self-love/tender-return', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-warmth', 3, 'Tender Warmth', 'Softness becomes strength when it is honest. As you move through today, protect your peace before you explain it away.', 'Self-love often begins as a quieter conversation, not a grand breakthrough. If it feels supportive, allow your standards to include compassion, not only discipline.', 'self-love', 'openness', 'self-love/tender-warmth', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-permission', 4, 'Tender Permission', 'The way you speak to yourself sets the tone for the day. For now, allow enough gentleness for your nervous system to believe you.', 'What you accept with compassion can finally begin to settle. In this moment, give yourself one moment of care before you give your energy away.', 'self-love', 'renewal', 'self-love/tender-permission', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-heartlight', 5, 'Tender Heartlight', 'You do not need to perform ease in order to deserve it. Offer yourself the same patience you keep giving away.', 'The permission to rest, feel, and begin again is part of your dignity. Let your next step feel warm enough to continue.', 'self-love', 'protection', 'self-love/tender-heartlight', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-embrace', 6, 'Tender Embrace', 'Notice what relaxes your body when no one is watching. Let your inner world feel less crowded and more kind.', 'The heart opens more easily when it does not feel judged for being human. For now, trust that small acts of gentleness can still change your day.', 'self-love', 'self-trust', 'self-love/tender-embrace', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-bloom', 7, 'Tender Bloom', 'Care becomes clearer when you stop withholding it from yourself. As you move through today, protect your peace before you explain it away.', 'A steadier relationship with yourself is built through repeated moments of honesty and care. If it feels supportive, choose language that leaves you feeling safe inside your own mind.', 'self-love', 'soft reset', 'self-love/tender-bloom', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'tender-worth', 8, 'Tender Worth', 'There is wisdom in treating your heart like something precious. For now, allow enough gentleness for your nervous system to believe you.', 'Your softness is most powerful when it is rooted in respect for your own needs. In this moment, notice where your body is asking for kindness, not correction.', 'self-love', 'quiet confidence', 'self-love/tender-worth', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'self-love'), 'radiant-mirror', 9, 'Radiant Mirror', 'You are allowed to meet yourself with less pressure today. Offer yourself the same patience you keep giving away.', 'Inner kindness changes the pace of healing because it removes the need to fight yourself. Return to what helps you feel held rather than evaluated.', 'self-love', 'openness', 'self-love/radiant-mirror', true),
