((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-window', 63, 'Clear Window', 'Clarity often arrives after you stop forcing a conclusion. Ask what feels true before asking what looks impressive.', 'Your inner guidance becomes sharper when you stop rewarding confusion with endless attention. Release the need to make the perfect choice before making the truthful one.', 'clarity', 'grounded action', 'clarity/clear-window', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-signal', 64, 'Clear Signal', 'Choose the question that makes your mind feel quieter, not louder. The next truth may be simpler than the fear around it.', 'Discernment is a practice of honoring what consistently brings coherence. For now, choose one honest next step instead of waiting for the whole map.', 'clarity', 'discernment', 'clarity/clear-signal', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-compass', 65, 'Clear Compass', 'Confusion loses power when you return to what is essential. As you move through today, name the thing you know before you collect another opinion.', 'Clarity deepens when you reduce the emotional static around the decision in front of you. If it feels supportive, clear one distraction and listen again.', 'clarity', 'quiet confidence', 'clarity/clear-compass', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-horizon', 66, 'Clear Horizon', 'You already know more than the noise around you suggests. For now, give yourself permission to see the pattern as it is.', 'A grounded choice usually feels cleaner in the body than a performative one. In this moment, write down what already feels known so it can stop circling.', 'clarity', 'fresh perspective', 'clarity/clear-horizon', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-answer', 67, 'Clear Answer', 'A calmer mind can hear what urgency keeps interrupting. Ask what feels true before asking what looks impressive.', 'When you simplify the question, the next step can reveal itself without drama. Trust what remains true after the overthinking settles.', 'clarity', 'inner knowing', 'clarity/clear-answer', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'clear-blueprint', 68, 'Clear Blueprint', 'Choose the question that makes your mind feel quieter, not louder. The answer you need may be waiting beneath the extra story.', 'Truth often becomes visible through stillness, because it does not need to compete to be real. For now, follow what gives your mind and body the same answer.', 'clarity', 'clean focus', 'clarity/clear-blueprint', true),
