((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-garden', 94, 'Golden Garden', 'Abundance grows more easily in spaces that are open, honest, and well tended. Let enoughness change the way you choose today.', 'A well-supported life is often built through grounded choices repeated with trust. Tend what is already growing before you chase more.', 'abundance', 'expansion', 'abundance/golden-garden', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-current', 95, 'Golden Current', 'Notice where your energy wants to expand without strain. Receiving becomes possible when you stop shrinking to feel safe.', 'There is wisdom in building slowly where your roots can actually hold the growth. For now, say yes to one form of support that feels clean and mutual.', 'abundance', 'openness', 'abundance/golden-current', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-harvest', 96, 'Golden Harvest', 'There is value in what comes slowly and stays rooted. As you move through today, allow support to be practical, visible, and real.', 'Abundance becomes sustainable when your nervous system no longer confuses receiving with risk. If it feels supportive, notice what opportunity feels nourishing rather than depleting.', 'abundance', 'grounded action', 'abundance/golden-harvest', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-gate', 97, 'Golden Gate', 'Your life can hold more good than your old scarcity stories expect. For now, let your standards rise with your capacity to receive.', 'Prosperity asks for openness, but it also asks for stewardship and self-respect. In this moment, let your next financial or energetic choice reflect enoughness.', 'abundance', 'renewal', 'abundance/golden-gate', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-pulse', 98, 'Golden Pulse', 'Support may arrive through steadiness before it arrives through scale. Let enoughness change the way you choose today.', 'Expansion feels more stable when it is connected to values instead of urgency. Treat your resources like something sacred and alive.', 'abundance', 'magnetism', 'abundance/golden-pulse', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-reserve', 99, 'Golden Reserve', 'Notice where your energy wants to expand without strain. Prosperity is allowed to feel calm instead of chaotic.', 'The energy of enoughness creates cleaner decisions than the energy of lack. For now, choose stability that can widen over time.', 'abundance', 'receiving', 'abundance/golden-reserve', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'golden-bloom', 100, 'Golden Bloom', 'You do not need to grip tightly to be well supported. As you move through today, allow support to be practical, visible, and real.', 'What multiplies in your life is often what you are willing to treat as worthy of care. If it feels supportive, practice receiving without immediately making yourself smaller.', 'abundance', 'expansion', 'abundance/golden-bloom', true),
