((select id from decks where slug = 'abundance'), 'open-reserve', 115, 'Open Reserve', 'Notice where your energy wants to expand without strain. Prosperity is allowed to feel calm instead of chaotic.', 'The energy of enoughness creates cleaner decisions than the energy of lack. For now, choose stability that can widen over time.', 'abundance', 'renewal', 'abundance/open-reserve', true),
