((select id from decks where slug = 'inner-reset'), 'quiet-pause', 186, 'Quiet Pause', 'Rest is part of your wisdom, not a reward for exhaustion. Choose what gives your body permission to unclench.', 'A rested spirit hears guidance more clearly than an overdriven one. Allow your next hour to contain more breathing room.', 'rest', 'soft reset', 'rest/quiet-pause', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'inner-reset'), 'quiet-exhale', 187, 'Quiet Exhale', 'Protect the moments that help you feel unhurried. A slower pace can be the most intelligent move available.', 'Gentle routines can become a powerful form of self-protection. For now, give yourself one unhurried pocket of time and do not defend it.', 'rest', 'restoration', 'rest/quiet-exhale', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'inner-reset'), 'quiet-sanctuary', 188, 'Quiet Sanctuary', 'Your body deserves moments that do not ask it to brace. As you move through today, allow enough softness for your breath to deepen.', 'Rest creates clarity because it gives your inner world enough room to settle. If it feels supportive, protect your energy as carefully as your time.', 'rest', 'protection', 'rest/quiet-sanctuary', true),
