((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'faithful-timing', 306, 'Faithful Timing', 'Trust grows when you stop demanding immediate proof from every step. A grounded pause can still be movement.', 'A season of waiting can still be deeply productive when it is shaping your readiness. Trust the preparation happening beneath the surface.', 'trust', 'divine timing', 'trust/faithful-timing', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'faithful-bridge', 307, 'Faithful Bridge', 'Notice where patience is creating more strength than urgency. You are still being guided, even when the full shape is not yet visible.', 'Patience carries power when it is paired with attentive presence. For now, let your next move come from steadiness rather than panic.', 'trust', 'surrender', 'trust/faithful-bridge', true),
((select id from decks where slug = 'cosmic-core'), 'faithful-knowing', 308, 'Faithful Knowing', 'What is unfolding for you does not always reveal itself all at once. As you move through today, allow your body to relax around what is not yet resolved.', 'Trust is built through repeated evidence that you can stay present without controlling everything. If it feels supportive, give your body one signal that it is safe to wait with grace.', 'trust', 'protection', 'trust/faithful-knowing', true),
